{"an8.17:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 8.17 ","an8.17:0.2":"2. Mahavagga ","an8.17:0.3":"Pathamabandhanasutta ","an8.17:1.1":"“Atthahi, bhikkhave, akarehi itthi purisam bandhati. ","an8.17:1.2":"Katamehi atthahi? ","an8.17:1.3":"Runnena, bhikkhave, itthi purisam bandhati; ","an8.17:1.4":"hasitena, bhikkhave, itthi purisam bandhati; ","an8.17:1.5":"bhanitena, bhikkhave, itthi purisam bandhati; ","an8.17:1.6":"akappena, bhikkhave, itthi purisam bandhati; ","an8.17:1.7":"vanabhangena, bhikkhave, itthi purisam bandhati; ","an8.17:1.8":"gandhena, bhikkhave, itthi purisam bandhati; ","an8.17:1.9":"rasena, bhikkhave, itthi purisam bandhati; ","an8.17:1.10":"phassena, bhikkhave, itthi purisam bandhati. ","an8.17:1.11":"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, atthahakarehi itthi purisam bandhati. ","an8.17:1.12":"Te, bhikkhave, satta subaddha, ye phassena baddha”ti. ","an8.17:1.13":"Sattamam. "}